      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p>For your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.bhSrjkuWxz2DQHXC]{Debilitating Trick}, you can try to stun your target. The target must succeed at a Fortitude save or be @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.CvsDp0GvojxiF2jz]{Stunned} until the start of your next turn. Once you’ve used this ability to try to stun a creature, it’s immune to your stunning shot for 24 hours. You must have the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.o2GDNS1g87yquIMS]{Staggering Shot} exploit to learn this exploit.</p>"
